<P>
Orange County wades into its second hundred years facing a <DATE>summer</DATE> that's filled 
with a wider range of arts and entertainment activities than ever. 
</P>
<P>
The Calendar staff of the <ORGANIZATION>Times Orange County Edition</ORGANIZATION> selects highlights among 
the hundreds of choices offered at the county's theaters, art museums, outdoor 
amphitheaters, concert halls, comedy clubs, movie theaters and elsewhere to 
stave off any <DATE>summer</DATE> doldrums that might dare to take roost. 
</P>
