* <PERSON>Yuri Temirkanov</PERSON> will lead the <LOCATION>Philadelphia Orchestra</LOCATION> in <ORGANIZATION>Tchaikovsky</ORGANIZATION>'s 
Symphony No. 1 and <ORGANIZATION>Prokofiev</ORGANIZATION>'s Symphony No. 5 at <TIME>8 p.m.</TIME> on <DATE>Thursday</DATE> at the 
